summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Seattle Center Department; adding a new section, Section 17.16.015, to the Seattle Municipal Code to establish fees and charges and terms and conditions for use of certain Seattle Center facilities, and repealing SMC 17.16.020 and SMC 17.16.025 as well as Ordinances 109490, 110896, 111433, and 112031 in connection therewith.
